##########################
upkeeper 0.01
##########################

Run

    ./configure

and then

    make

to compile this.

To run a quick demo, do

    cd demo
    ./demo-setup.sh

then open a new terminal with

    cd ..
    cd uptop
    ./uptop

and type

    ./demo-down
    ./demo-up

in the old terminal, to watch the upkeeper dashboard update.

